ss().getInterfaces(), handler);\n  }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777660206540}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_MR4ZXYcRXsckNs1nk760lXHN|fc_0071ea2d95a871970169f4f12e5218819ea594597445cfc634", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "tests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/AnnotatedClassTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/AnnotatedConstructorTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/AnnotatedFieldTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/AnnotatedMethodTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/ArrayBuildersTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/ClassUtilInnerEnumTypeLocatorTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/ClassUtilTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/Htrace_coreTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/JsonValueSerializerTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/LogFactoryImplTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/LogFactoryTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/LogSourceTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/OptionalHandlerFactoryTest.java\ntests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java